    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what? taking it with a high fat meal helps? i didnt know that. so if i just take the simvastatin with breakfast and then take my antibiotic a few hours later in the afternoon, is that enough to make it safe? i just want to be sure i dont have to go to the doctor for something minor.",
